We can't let him find out.

5
00:00:05,360 --> 00:00:05,880
Hey!

6
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:07,620
I want to talk to Benson!

7
00:00:08,119 --> 00:00:09,180
Whew, that was close.

8
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,600
Wait!

9
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:13,080
I want to talk!

10
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,460
