11
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,440
Didn't you hear me calling you?

12
00:00:21,625 --> 00:00:22,760
Oh, hey Muscle Man.

13
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:24,380
How's it going?

14
00:00:24,540 --> 00:00:25,660
What do you ladies care?

